{"h54ac0629g4a8cg445bg9239g5861a9ae3089": ["Escape!? Escape!", "d17d3d8e-cf4a-48cd-a5ab-de0083110785", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Ball.html", "e4bba967-f9d9-1cbc-d368-e83f6d1a216a"], "h274a8eb4g16b5g455ega510gda82baceb159": ["Burning! Feathers burning!", "d17d3d8e-cf4a-48cd-a5ab-de0083110785", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Ball.html", "374f9e2f-b879-883a-7563-af7b791c7f7a"], "h9caa9c0ag3420g4975gafaeg37275dc355a6": ["You! Help? HELP!", "d17d3d8e-cf4a-48cd-a5ab-de0083110785", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Ball.html", "75c36a3f-a499-8d36-c950-765fd7b8dce0"], "h917da671g9ce4g4e21gb4a0gccbac41cac32": ["<i>Urge her to attack them.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Ball.html", "54693c9a-ad69-fff0-132a-cc635b10c76e"], "h29dddcb8gadecg4973gabc8g4d5cb823d070": ["No. Too many goblins. Too many dead before me!", "d17d3d8e-cf4a-48cd-a5ab-de0083110785", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Ball.html", "9d0aeefc-b939-374c-951d-12e6c2559f4f"], "h8a620dfagd689g405aga455g40ad6a373592": ["Yes! Bite and claw and tear and bite!", "d17d3d8e-cf4a-48cd-a5ab-de0083110785", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Ball.html", "26412eb8-7c68-adf1-df17-a49509493fe1"], "h4013b2b9gb180g4883g8630gaae083a41108": ["Wild things do not beg for help. They <i>protect</i> themselves.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Ball.html", "3eb7dd82-5e07-5096-5250-5b534ffd0601"], "hd4816338g424bg4dfeg9954g6d31e946cb7e": ["What's wrong?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Ball.html", "8f3ea0fd-2e0d-7523-c77d-a3be91192d86"], "h885a676cg4982g4e1agb807gc8924365d796": ["Tired. Frightened. A game to the featherless ones - but not a game! Not a game!", "d17d3d8e-cf4a-48cd-a5ab-de0083110785", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Ball.html", "24b27391-dbd9-97c0-4098-5c7c161a607e"], "h35b644e3g2daag4c2ag8b19ga978a1bb62a5": ["I'll help. Just run through the posts, and you'll be free.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Ball.html", "bb4d6f3e-43c1-b357-0e75-e7494bdc382e"], "h4274d9dbgef33g4bdagb062gab22559c4334": ["Free? Free!? FREE!", "d17d3d8e-cf4a-48cd-a5ab-de0083110785", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Ball.html", "71509cd0-a3e9-d769-5e97-5d455c2c9d69"], "h49c408cagb54ag48c3gb023g0d1824f10639": ["Oh shut up and <i>play.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Ball.html", "5ef4dcc7-a64e-c6f9-96f0-df22b62b9672"], "h7ac76f46ge9efg4309g886bg7cb8244e9a4d": ["Mad! Featherless ones are mad!", "d17d3d8e-cf4a-48cd-a5ab-de0083110785", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Ball.html", "39491c81-a378-b997-ceb1-076580e35d2d"], "h302af696g5dd8g4fa3gbcd1gb859f6bf32aa": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Ball.html", "8976d019-26b6-cfb9-5e4b-a90af4821af7"], "h7f233ee4g6e5fg4af6gbf6cg8cfb7739699c": ["Tired. Lie down. But don't want to <i>burn.</i>", "d17d3d8e-cf4a-48cd-a5ab-de0083110785", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Ball.html", "9cbb447b-5d6d-b9ff-f835-d93b016f74bd"], "haeb68c6aga2feg4fbegaa7egb62344e46b48": ["You'll be free just as soon as you run through the posts.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Ball.html", "e4d2492b-97c7-cebe-0476-f4557422f5d8"], "h6024694bg96adg4779gb2e3g4f7b28fd32f2": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Ball.html", "fcd878f9-435c-48c8-c712-c273a3066607"], "he2aa1963g1ea7g4432g92afg5da8025e5185": ["*Squawk!*", "d17d3d8e-cf4a-48cd-a5ab-de0083110785", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Ball.html", "8e5b1a56-696b-9e72-bf63-f1aede5b06f3"], "hfd199e68g0017g47a6gb021g01a5438d6ecb": ["*Squawk!*", "d17d3d8e-cf4a-48cd-a5ab-de0083110785", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Ball.html", "fb6599db-857b-e713-3931-f66dfcd6cd31"], "h3ab07212g076bg4835gb5c9gcc08283ce06f": ["*The chicken's head bobs, eyes darting around at the leering goblin faces. She's terrified.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Ball.html", "4f1eca13-6cd1-16ae-0c70-c247f6819b90"], "h3ddbf87bga794g4d7dg9a66g94b18407ae7a": ["<i>Urge her to attack them.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Ball.html", "3b727baa-bd6e-0d67-6b17-3facf4a4cfeb"], "h035620beg219eg48f5g9a71ge1cb314af214": ["*She shrinks from your voice - just another leering face sent to torment her.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Ball.html", "c4625841-c9f7-8d2f-d1b3-bfdbc6a1641e"], "h18b8b497g3430g46b7ga26cgb51d7713456b": ["*She meets your eye, and the fear there hardens into rage. She gathers herself.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Ball.html", "0be8a490-9f7f-f19b-e9cd-b972c9fcc213"], "h3cebbc01gdf24g4a2bga059g0c5dcf2fc240": ["<i>Shoo her towards the posts.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Ball.html", "d5a613ef-7064-8857-33af-6497ac51e136"], "h7ef2c24dg0a02g4cc6gb399g71253cd67d79": ["*Squawk!*", "d17d3d8e-cf4a-48cd-a5ab-de0083110785", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Ball.html", "ede5d1e6-6634-d204-6ab3-397359d4f9ce"], "h13d76b20gb1e1g4cc0gbda3gb8f2d52bb9d9": ["*She shies away in fear, not understanding.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Ball.html", "98ddbdd4-a1bb-0ca8-528a-8017f9f81edb"], "h302fab14ge70cg49b0g8d36gcb49f5a92d9e": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Ball.html", "5ffec6c4-475b-eb26-febc-984fbef3d6bc"]}